.index-main-flame
  .index-main-flame-all
    .index-main-flame-all-box
      .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_text
        購入を確定しますか？
      .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content
        .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item
          .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item_box
            .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item_box-image
              = image_tag("#{@product.images.first.image}", class: 'image-fot_index')
            .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item_box-detail
              .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item_box-detail_name
                = @product.name
              .index-main-flame-all-box-buy_content-item_box-detail_price
                = ('¥' + @product.price.to_s(:delimited) + '(税込み)')
      .index-main-flame-all-box-choice
        .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-flame
          .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-payment
            .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-payment-text
              支払い方法:クレジットカード
            .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-payment-registration
              - if @default_card_information.blank?
                %br /
              - else
                -#以下カード情報を表示
                = "**** **** **** " + @default_card_information.last4
                - exp_month = @default_card_information.exp_month.to_s
                - exp_year = @default_card_information.exp_year.to_s.slice(2,3)
                = exp_month + " / " + exp_year

          .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-buy
            .index-main-flame-all-box-choice-buy-button
              = form_tag(action: :pay, method: :post) do
                %button.button 購入する